==Useful Info==
'''Molten gargoyles''' are the rarest of the [[gargoyle]] types. They aren't much stronger than a standard gargoyle, but their attacks inflict additional [[fire]] damage, and their [[Bolt of Magma]] can hurt. They can be found in [[Gehenna]], the [[Desolation of Salt]], some [[volcano]] layouts, and certain fire-themed [[vault]]s.

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*Fire resistance will help reduce the damage you take.
*Unlike [[gargoyle (monster)|regular gargoyle]]s or [[war gargoyle]]s, molten gargoyles are not susceptible to [[LRD]].

==History==
*Prior to [[0.14]], molten gargoyles knew no spells, wielded no weapons, and were mostly harmless to anything but your scrolls.
